{"tid":263560,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【美食車跳船】蘇錦樑認部分地點不理想 會引入新景點","createTime":"2017-05-30T06:28:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-30T12:19:30.000Z","uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"173bb6fa58dc56409162e56a8869e8718bc38079","tid":263560,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T06:28:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170530/large/1496122962_4355.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170530%2Flarge%2F1496122962_4355.jpg&h=ffe46ceb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n繼華星冰室後，藝人谷祖琳的甜品店「小甜谷」亦宣佈退出美食車先導計劃。被問會否影響其他經營者信心，商務及經濟發展局局長蘇錦樑回應指，有經營者的業務不錯，但承認部分地點不理想，當局會引入新景點，並給予更多優惠措施，方便營運者接觸市民和旅客。<br />\n<br />\n蘇錦樑認為每個營辦商對營運方法、成本和風險承擔有不同看法，他表示理解和尊重，強調當局一直完善營商環境，盡量配合營辦商的需要﹛重申當局有替補機制。<br />\n<br />\n旅遊事務署指出，小甜谷因在籌備美食車時有技術上困難，已3次延長其取得營運牌照限期，其空缺將由The Butchers Club取替；而早前退出的華星冰室，其空缺將由擦餐飽取替。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56760453&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170530\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56760453%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170530&d=xmI6ZfB0VaIidVIJLTIytr%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=15b76667\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56760453%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170530&h=dccbe714\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56760453&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170530</a>"},{"pid":"df99f71d756d0fb3555bb5377b25baeae9e4eb08","tid":263560,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T06:33:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c43ff026fc22e7a406e22a34b16789aeff5c58d7","tid":263560,"uid":41116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T12:19:30.000Z","msg":"去到邊都要比人抽水分成<br />\n搞到d 野仲貴撚過舖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}